column5: SBOT just so you guys dont panic sell Ive played merger votes before They generally dont tell you right away After hours maybe but I doubt it They tally everything and get a pr ready then announce Most likely tomorrow But Ive gotten stopped out before because it only takes a few well placed shorts and people will assume its bad news then sell Then it dips and shorters cover Meanwhile your shares get basically stolen for cheap Some of you are better off turning your screens off until tomorrow but GLTU anyway Although almost ALWAYS merger votes are approved because it creates excitement and stock price movement Always a good thing
